{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015dmeqaegm71Ki8DKGWdBqQ","type":"tool_result","content":"   580→**3. Stale branch cleanup across repos**\n   581→- promptlibrary: deleted 6 local + 1 remote stale branches\n   582→- pezantTools: pruned 5 stale remote tracking refs\n   583→- trustedCircle: deleted 3 local + 5 remote stale branches\n   584→\n   585→### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n   586→- **trustedCircle**: Search & filtering done (Tier 1 #2). Remaining Tier 1: follow system (#1), review detail page (#3), better seed data (#4)\n   587→- **pezantTools**: Still has ejs 3→5, multer 1→2, tailwindcss 3→4 (lower priority)\n   588→- **All repos**: Clean branch state, tests passing, CI active\n   589→\n   590→---\n   591→\n   592→## 2026-03-20 — Run 25\n   593→\n   594→### What was done\n   595→\n   596→**trustedCircle — Review detail page (Tier 1 roadmap feature) (PR #16, auto-merged)**\n   597→- Added `GET /api/reviews/:id` API endpoint — returns review with enriched reviewer (including categories), category, and up to 4 related reviews from same reviewer in same category\n   598→- Created `ReviewDetailPage.tsx` with full review body, larger star rating, category badge, date, location, reviewer attribution card with avatar and category badges, and \"More from @handle\" related reviews section\n   599→- Made all `ReviewCard` components clickable — navigates to `/review/:id` from homepage, person page, category page, and search results\n   600→- Added `line-clamp-3` to review body in cards for cleaner grid layout\n   601→- Reviewer handle in cards uses `stopPropagation` to still navigate to person page\n   602→- Route ordering fix: `/api/reviews/recent` registered before `/api/reviews/:id` to prevent \"recent\" matching as an ID\n   603→- 5 new API tests covering full response shape, 404, empty related, self-exclusion, and 4-item limit (40 total, all passing)\n   604→- Build verified, Playwright visual verification passed (homepage cards, review detail page layout)\n   605→\n   606→### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n   607→- **trustedCircle**: Review detail page done (Tier 1 #3). Remaining Tier 1: follow system (#1), better seed data (#4)\n   608→- **pezantTools**: Still has ejs 3→5, multer 1→2, tailwindcss 3→4 (lower priority)\n   609→- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active\n   610→\n   611→---\n   612→\n   613→## 2026-03-20 — Run 26\n   614→\n   615→### What was done\n   616→\n   617→**trustedCircle — Follow system (Tier 1 #1 roadmap feature) (PR #17/#18, auto-merged)**\n   618→- New `followers` table with `(user_id, reviewer_id)` unique constraint and indexes on both columns\n   619→- Anonymous user identity via localStorage UUID (no auth required)\n   620→- `POST /api/follow/:handle` — follow a reviewer (idempotent, returns 201 on first follow, 200 if already following)\n   621→- `DELETE /api/follow/:handle` — unfollow a reviewer (idempotent)\n   622→- `GET /api/following?userId=` — returns list of followed reviewer IDs (for UI state)\n   623→- `GET /api/circle?userId=` — feed of reviews from followed reviewers (limit 50, chronological, with reviewer and category enrichment)\n   624→- Follow/unfollow button on person pages — moss green pill, toggles to outline \"Following\" state with hover color change\n   625→- \"My Circle\" page at `/circle` — reviews from followed people, empty state with icon, messaging, and \"Browse people\" CTA\n   626→- Heart icon nav link in header between Home and People\n   627→- `useUserId` hook generates/persists stable UUID in localStorage\n   628→- Client API methods for follow, unfollow, getFollowing, getCircle\n   629→- 15 new API tests covering follow, unfollow, idempotency, user isolation, circle feed with single/multiple follows, empty states\n   630→- 55 total tests (was 40), all passing\n   631→- Build verified, Playwright visual verification passed (homepage nav, person page follow button, circle empty state)\n   632→\n   633→### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n   634→- **trustedCircle**: Follow system done (Tier 1 #1). Remaining Tier 1: better seed data (#4). All Tier 1 features now complete except seed data.\n   635→- **trustedCircle**: No staging environment — merging to main is sufficient\n   636→- **pezantTools**: Still has ejs 3→5, multer 1→2, tailwindcss 3→4 (lower priority)\n   637→- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active\n   638→\n   639→---"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd6ea26a-cb05-47a5-8060-bb9857e501ca","uuid":"23136310-f6d4-4b6e-a56c-0ecfe13b3f89","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:31:05.600Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"REDACTED_REPOS_ROOT/autonomousDev/logs/progress.md","content":"**3. Stale branch cleanup across repos**\n- promptlibrary: deleted 6 local + 1 remote stale branches\n- pezantTools: pruned 5 stale remote tracking refs\n- trustedCircle: deleted 3 local + 5 remote stale branches\n\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Search & filtering done (Tier 1 #2). Remaining Tier 1: follow system (#1), review detail page (#3), better seed data (#4)\n- **pezantTools**: Still has ejs 3→5, multer 1→2, tailwindcss 3→4 (lower priority)\n- **All repos**: Clean branch state, tests passing, CI active\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 — Run 25\n\n### What was done\n\n**trustedCircle — Review detail page (Tier 1 roadmap feature) (PR #16, auto-merged)**\n- Added `GET /api/reviews/:id` API endpoint — returns review with enriched reviewer (including categories), category, and up to 4 related reviews from same reviewer in same category\n- Created `ReviewDetailPage.tsx` with full review body, larger star rating, category badge, date, location, reviewer attribution card with avatar and category badges, and \"More from @handle\" related reviews section\n- Made all `ReviewCard` components clickable — navigates to `/review/:id` from homepage, person page, category page, and search results\n- Added `line-clamp-3` to review body in cards for cleaner grid layout\n- Reviewer handle in cards uses `stopPropagation` to still navigate to person page\n- Route ordering fix: `/api/reviews/recent` registered before `/api/reviews/:id` to prevent \"recent\" matching as an ID\n- 5 new API tests covering full response shape, 404, empty related, self-exclusion, and 4-item limit (40 total, all passing)\n- Build verified, Playwright visual verification passed (homepage cards, review detail page layout)\n\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Review detail page done (Tier 1 #3). Remaining Tier 1: follow system (#1), better seed data (#4)\n- **pezantTools**: Still has ejs 3→5, multer 1→2, tailwindcss 3→4 (lower priority)\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 — Run 26\n\n### What was done\n\n**trustedCircle — Follow system (Tier 1 #1 roadmap feature) (PR #17/#18, auto-merged)**\n- New `followers` table with `(user_id, reviewer_id)` unique constraint and indexes on both columns\n- Anonymous user identity via localStorage UUID (no auth required)\n- `POST /api/follow/:handle` — follow a reviewer (idempotent, returns 201 on first follow, 200 if already following)\n- `DELETE /api/follow/:handle` — unfollow a reviewer (idempotent)\n- `GET /api/following?userId=` — returns list of followed reviewer IDs (for UI state)\n- `GET /api/circle?userId=` — feed of reviews from followed reviewers (limit 50, chronological, with reviewer and category enrichment)\n- Follow/unfollow button on person pages — moss green pill, toggles to outline \"Following\" state with hover color change\n- \"My Circle\" page at `/circle` — reviews from followed people, empty state with icon, messaging, and \"Browse people\" CTA\n- Heart icon nav link in header between Home and People\n- `useUserId` hook generates/persists stable UUID in localStorage\n- Client API methods for follow, unfollow, getFollowing, getCircle\n- 15 new API tests covering follow, unfollow, idempotency, user isolation, circle feed with single/multiple follows, empty states\n- 55 total tests (was 40), all passing\n- Build verified, Playwright visual verification passed (homepage nav, person page follow button, circle empty state)\n\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Follow system done (Tier 1 #1). Remaining Tier 1: better seed data (#4). All Tier 1 features now complete except seed data.\n- **trustedCircle**: No staging environment — merging to main is sufficient\n- **pezantTools**: Still has ejs 3→5, multer 1→2, tailwindcss 3→4 (lower priority)\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active\n\n---","numLines":60,"startLine":580,"totalLines":1055}}}
